headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Car Meet Prize Ride: Shitzu Hakuchou Drag
content:
Determined LS Car Meet members who place in the top three in five Pursuit Races this week will get a Shitzu Hakuchou Drag to ride and customize to their tastes.

To unlock access to the LS Car Meet, head over to see Mimi in Cypress Flats. You can find her location by locating the LS Car Meet icon on the GTA Online Map.
